{"tid":633837,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【亞視永恆】亞視上市！協盛協豐改名「亞洲電視」","createTime":"2018-04-18T15:54:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-18T17:29:10.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"716d11f8ddfd231f4ed5a732fb1f15d3c572267f","tid":633837,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T15:54:12.000Z","msg":"[img]<a href=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180417/large/1523956277_6ca6.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180417%2Flarge%2F1523956277_6ca6.jpg&d=GKafLAlYqJrlEtR9f%2FxvzXadZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=5bcf3037\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180417/large/1523956277_6ca6.jpg</a><br />\n[/img]<br />\n協盛協豐（707）今日公佈，改名為「亞洲電視控股有限公司」，股份簡稱亦改為「亞洲電視控股」，股份代號則沒變。此外，公司標誌的標示已由原本的標誌，改成印有亞視名字的標示。公司網站將由「<a href=\"http://www.co-prosperity.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.co-prosperity.com.hk&d=GKafLAlYqJrlEtR9f%2FxvzXadZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=923679da\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.co-prosperity.com.hk</a>」更改為「<a href=\"http://www.atvgroup.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.atvgroup.com.hk&d=GKafLAlYqJrlEtR9f%2FxvzXadZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=dd47707e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.atvgroup.com.hk</a>」，上述變動將於4月20日生效。<br />\n<br />\n不過，協盛協豐上周公布，集團管理層已開始獲得有限及不完整的亞洲電視賬簿及記錄，但因有限制存取和不完整記錄，尚未完全控制亞視。<br />\n協盛協豐今日收報0.295元，升1.7%，暫時成交金額247.2萬元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180417/58084311\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180417%2F58084311&d=GKafLAlYqJrlEtR9f%2FxvzXadZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=11edca96\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180417%2F58084311&h=565a3118\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180417/58084311</a>"},{"pid":"f8548f12ad94e4eeda38c1c1c6d3b2dda13f92f1","tid":633837,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T15:54:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180417/large/1523956277_6ca6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180417%2Flarge%2F1523956277_6ca6.jpg&h=31314575&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e364bb353a42cc24146132bd7f1a2c493163a2cd","tid":633837,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T16:43:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce6fb99acb205b1d2a8e74307c92a51bde39f6de","tid":633837,"uid":6030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T16:47:10.000Z","msg":"封閉式開台"},{"pid":"43e70d201dea07feae243f7ad439cf63c5bfd6e7","tid":633837,"uid":158572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T16:50:41.000Z","msg":"買殼?"},{"pid":"a2ff81c6ad1b997b022e7f188451db182949c79a","tid":633837,"uid":6347,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"43e70d201dea07feae243f7ad439cf63c5bfd6e7","tid":633837,"uid":158572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T16:50:41.000Z","msg":"買殼?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T16:56:03.000Z","msg":"又係大陸佬炒殼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfd75930fb74f66df2829d321e530bee4da9e85d","tid":633837,"uid":10249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T16:58:22.000Z","msg":"岸鳩無極限 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97bcc937ca8f5da9ca2055b0ba57b8c108c900c2","tid":633837,"uid":116330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T16:58:48.000Z","msg":"2015年下半年，我們開始拯救已瀕臨破產清盤邊緣的香港亞洲電視，一家具有60年歷史的老牌香港電視台。公司看好數字媒體和娛樂產業的前景，於2016年4月簽訂了股權買賣協議，收購52.42% 的 ATV股權，並與ATV前控股股東及其附屬公司及ATV前雇員簽署了債務轉讓協議。<br />\n<br />\n2017年4月24日，公司持續挽救ATV的努力初見成效，法院同意清盤人離場。我們通過旗下全資子公司星鉑企業有限公司對ATV的債權人進行債務償還安排。我們在ATV董事會委任了幾名董事, 擴展了ATV的管理團隊，並為這家老牌香港電視台重新運作積極招攬人才，使ATV煥然一新。2017年9月12日，債務償還計畫於ATV債務人會議中獲得通過，並於2017年12月12日，聆訊獲法庭批准及其後於2018年1月8日，獲法庭頒令撤回對ATV發出的清盤呈請。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好撚偉大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f2b2471df586f1b8baeb10c6b30a9a9effe7df5","tid":633837,"uid":139150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T17:05:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/eDpqJqFnJlU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FeDpqJqFnJlU&d=GKafLAlYqJrlEtR9f%2FxvzXadZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=b425c684\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/eDpqJqFnJlU</a>"},{"pid":"dce235997822aa69ffa5defc6676076a265494bf","tid":633837,"uid":29851,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T17:29:10.000Z","msg":"王精真係好撚on9，一早用呢個方法又可以玩埋向下炒，長炒長有。唔知做乜要自己抬錢又做埋啲小丑戲係到獻世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}